Find An Expert

     This database of health economics researchers contains the name,
     contact information, brief profile, and research interest keywords
     of experts in specific areas of research.

     To find an expert in your field of interest, please search the
     database by typing in keywords. You may also search by last name or
     state, and view the entire database.

